    "For more details, refer to the ANLI GitHub repository.",
    "e-SNLI (Explainable Stanford Natural Language Inference) (Camburu et al., 2018): Extends the SNLI dataset by providing human-annotated explanations for NLI decisions, assessing models on inference and explanation generation.",
